text: This is the BBC. This podcast is supported by advertising outside the UK. This Leicester Dollywkjoukjou for BBC Radio Nengale. This is Leicester Dolok Geunce from BBC Radio Nongale. In this is Leicester Dollyggy Learer, Leighur in MacGelaine. This Leitjitre three-hid in 6. Gjerk. in MacGillain, this is 1,300 in 182. I'm a dull a chur-cureach to the school of my own Mary and the brahe of Colham. There is a-isuner in the Rahn. Fagmary a conchurch of the new, in the way, goodrich. Chahe the blanichan shakad Chathafas Marriariev. There's one Chariachka and there the Finister for Donbenam Raborst. It's six years the boyca the I and charoe hein pausta the small. But charo suria a un-etor the E and he'll go to the same paulstah in small. But, charo saw a rhea on etterra, fat jiruch in the Jow Charrichin. Rannick Mary out of four years a year, Chiquel the Parnton, the rick mary on in the day, it was a rickrocherach, but charoa a crea awns in Opeh, Riechee, a hula behehachir. Glea one chath, marfecht. For Aungu-Aum Figeaulov and a fackle in Tai Fadul. Hearoffice Ech Dunya, caroie a dole. Rannickie Ous and a faqal in the tae, Faddle, charrufis I could doon, caroie a doll. Rannick ewee Ushesquat, there Rabberst, Cookeat, there's a girl in o'er, and it's a keely o'errish. Chahe'am laa and washae, and was ma'erie in theenag awnsen lepy. Hick a rabberst, Husty, Jain'suey Raine'sueya, J'ah Kare, Gainikere, Keth Nakhir I, ch'erichin, I, charrich me, not a rakeal-ackam, but one garrich. Anjianu Ruttikin'on. No, hushed-rubberst, Routzebe. Curth to love for mychlewes'ek. Reina that, and hugh came a lot of Jarek. Leve, hoistie, have me, I'm a-isun-you-ruthic in Gaw-Irude-on. When I'm at least I'm in English and Tye, Meren, a hula-datt on the man of the town dune but the genu un-ruth-one the root-go. The cur of clack-feck in Cairn the Hogue of Cicahm, clach on the Cumaglia, with Cicr Fakhlun or her, Callum and Mary. Goulde? That's the year of Jainu, Y. Dahl o'all in that, Choucheal Mary and the Tew is fairan-ehick a rick Fahmari there's a carer on the way fast to the o'er and churrabort clach on the comag Cria to the coombe the huagach he said he'd Father Facklan that Cullam and Madi CRIE, in Ciam, the Hoagach. Screefjee o'er, Fakhlun, Gou Callum, and Madi. Leav Rabberst the Laird Pick Jarek Jereck, Tewmuth Fisick, Eintach, Eater Mari and Cullam. Chathdeggou Ritunia, my own. Chahar, one eunctach in the Chalachan, the Chouacch when there was a t'allu book-fluch chunic do you lollack in Cush Anasach Fasch in Oweeah Mari. There's tea to the harsdakin a yee in O'Oae Maree. There Chae to the harsaken a year to the chus each the thing, that's that they were a view, but there's a fin he's that's that there on the Gauton Uye, GUNE to Chutikin to Chutigin my Ler Vick Yere, and the Chon to sound my A'er and the Brather. Gereach, Mose de Chouachele he did she my own the Wunter in Ache Natcha. Inasm Vich Nell Muts D'Euchel in it, she Senever innoose-Fich Nail. Moucchal Isha, heen she do inouyeos, because then there was a chlach anosuchin, on the Cumbag Cria, on the club of Vela.
